### Infrastructure Layer

#### [NEW] [PrismaBattleRepository.ts](file:///d:/interviewUndo/apps/backend-api/src/infrastructure/database/repositories/PrismaBattleRepository.ts)
Prisma implementation of `IBattleRepository`.

#### [NEW] [RedisMatchmakingService.ts](file:///d:/interviewUndo/apps/backend-api/src/infrastructure/cache/RedisMatchmakingService.ts)
Redis-backed matchmaking using **Sorted Sets**:
- Key: `matchmaking:{difficulty}:{category}` — Score = join timestamp, Value = userId
- `joinQueue`: `ZADD` the user
- `findMatch`: `ZPOPMIN` to dequeue the oldest waiting player (if it's not yourself)
- `leaveQueue`: `ZREM` the user
- Atomic operations via Redis Lua scripts to prevent race conditions

#### [NEW] [BattleTimerManager.ts](file:///d:/interviewUndo/apps/backend-api/src/infrastructure/cache/BattleTimerManager.ts)
Server-side timer manager using `setTimeout` + Redis for persistence:
- Stores `battle:{id}:startedAt` in Redis
- On expiry, publishes to Redis pub/sub channel `battle:timer_expired`
- Supports reconnection by recalculating remaining time from Redis

#### [NEW] [BattleSocketHandler.ts](file:///d:/interviewUndo/apps/backend-api/src/infrastructure/websocket/BattleSocketHandler.ts)
The core real-time handler — registered as a Socket.io **namespace** (`/battle`). Handles:

| Event (Client → Server) | Handler Logic |
|---|---|
| `battle:join_queue` | Calls `JoinMatchmaking` use case |
| `battle:leave_queue` | Calls `LeaveMatchmaking` use case |
| `battle:code_change` | Throttled broadcast of code snippet to opponent in room |
| `battle:cursor_move` | Broadcast cursor position to opponent |
| `battle:chat` | Persist to `BattleChat`, broadcast to room |
| `battle:submit` | Calls `SubmitBattleSolution` use case |
| `battle:forfeit` | Calls `ForfeitBattle` use case |
| `disconnect` | Grace period logic, or forfeit if timer expires |

| Event (Server → Client) | Payload |
|---|---|
| `battle:matched` | `{battleId, problem, opponent, durationSeconds}` |
| `battle:opponent_typing` | `{codePreview, cursorPosition, lineCount}` |
| `battle:chat_message` | `{from, message, timestamp}` |
| `battle:tick` | `{remainingSeconds}` (every 1s) |
| `battle:opponent_submitted` | `{submittedAt}` |
| `battle:submission_result` | `{passedCases, totalCases, runtime, status}` |
| `battle:ended` | `{winner, yourScore, opponentScore, results}` |
| `battle:opponent_disconnected` | `{gracePeriodSeconds}` |
| `battle:opponent_reconnected` | `{}` |

