## Data Flow Diagrams

### Matchmaking Flow (Redis)
```mermaid
graph LR
    P1["Player 1<br/>joins queue"] --> RS["Redis Sorted Set<br/>matchmaking:MEDIUM:JAVASCRIPT"]
    P2["Player 2<br/>joins queue"] --> RS
    RS -->|ZPOPMIN x2| MM["Matchmaker<br/>(atomically pops 2)"]
    MM --> BATTLE["Create Battle<br/>+ pick problem"]
    BATTLE --> EMIT["Emit battle:matched<br/>to both players"]
```

### Battle State Machine
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> WAITING: Player joins queue
    WAITING --> IN_PROGRESS: Match found, both connected
    WAITING --> CANCELLED: Player leaves queue
    IN_PROGRESS --> COMPLETED: Timer expires OR both submit
    IN_PROGRESS --> FORFEITED: Player disconnects (grace period expired)
    COMPLETED --> [*]
    CANCELLED --> [*]
    FORFEITED --> [*]
```

